    "Multi-modal and multi-source data used in HDT modeling, such as patient's medical data, are compassionate and involve security and privacy issues.",
    "Theft or misuse of these data may cause serious damage to users.",
    "For traditional ML, privacy protection is supported by digital signatures and data encryption.",
    "It guarantees the protection of personal data, but causes an additional burden on data processing and increases the processing delay [98].",
    "To overcome this problem, federated learning can be considered to apply to HDT to reduce the processing delay while privacy is protected."
